---
layout: layouts/base-finpay.njk
title: "Registration Confirmed! | Federal Benefits Workshop April 9, 2026 | Capital Wealth"
description: "You're confirmed for the April 9 Federal Employee Benefits Workshop at Weber State University. Download your SF-182 form and add the event to your calendar."
noindex: true
excludeFromSitemap: true
bodyClass: "confirmation-page"
---

<style>
/* Confirmation Page Styling - Premium Capital Wealth Brand */
.confirmation-page {
  background: var(--gray-50);
}

/* Hero Confirmation Section */
.confirmation-hero {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cw-primary), var(--cw-secondary));
  color: var(--white);
  padding: var(--space-20) 0;
  text-align: center;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.confirmation-hero::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  background: url('/assets/images/photos/federal/capitalwealth-federal-us-capitol-dome.jpg');
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  opacity: 0.1;
}

.confirmation-content {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.success-badge {
  background: var(--cw-orange);
  color: var(--white);
  padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-6);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  display: inline-block;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
}

.confirmation-hero h1 {
  font-size: 3rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--white);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  line-height: 1.1;
}

.confirmation-hero .subtitle {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  opacity: 0.95;
  font-weight: 400;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.check-email-notice {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: var(--space-6);
  margin: 0 auto;
  max-width: 500px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
}

.check-email-notice h3 {
  color: var(--cw-orange);
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  font-weight: 600;
}

/* Next Steps Section */
.next-steps-section {
  padding: var(--space-20) 0;
  background: var(--white);
}

.steps-header {
  text-align: center;
  max-width: 600px;
  margin: 0 auto var(--space-16);
}

.steps-header h2 {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  color: var(--cw-primary);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  font-weight: 700;
}

.steps-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-8);
  max-width: 1000px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.step-card {
  background: var(--gray-50);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: var(--space-8);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  position: relative;
  border-left: 4px solid var(--cw-orange);
}

.step-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  background: var(--white);
}

.step-number {
  position: absolute;
  top: -15px;
  left: var(--space-6);
  background: var(--cw-primary);
  color: var(--white);
  width: 40px;
  height: 40px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
}

.step-card h3 {
  color: var(--cw-primary);
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  margin-top: var(--space-3);
  font-weight: 600;
}

.step-card p {
  color: var(--gray-700);
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
}

.step-action {
  background: var(--cw-primary);
  color: var(--white);
  padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-6);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 600;
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--space-2);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
}

.step-action:hover {
  background: var(--cw-secondary);
  transform: translateY(-1px);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
}

/* Event Details Section */
.event-details-section {
  padding: var(--space-16) 0;
  background: var(--gray-50);
}

.event-details-content {
  max-width: 1000px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.event-details-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
}

.event-details-header h2 {
  font-size: 2.25rem;
  color: var(--cw-primary);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  font-weight: 700;
}

.details-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-6);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
}

.detail-item {
  background: var(--white);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: var(--space-6);
  text-align: center;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.detail-item:hover {
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.detail-icon {
  font-size: 2rem;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  color: var(--cw-orange);
}

.detail-label {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--cw-primary);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
}

.detail-value {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--gray-800);
  line-height: 1.4;
}

/* What to Expect Section */
.expect-section {
  background: var(--white);
  border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
  padding: var(--space-12);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
}

.expect-section h3 {
  font-size: 1.75rem;
  color: var(--cw-primary);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  font-weight: 600;
}

.expect-content {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: var(--space-8);
  align-items: start;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .expect-content {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
}

.expect-text p {
  color: var(--gray-700);
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  font-size: 1.05rem;
}

.expect-highlights {
  background: var(--gray-50);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: var(--space-6);
  border-left: 4px solid var(--cw-orange);
}

.expect-highlights h4 {
  color: var(--cw-primary);
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  font-weight: 600;
}

.highlight-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: start;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  color: var(--gray-700);
}

.highlight-check {
  color: var(--cw-orange);
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-right: var(--space-3);
  margin-top: 2px;
}

/* Contact Section */
.contact-section {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cw-primary), var(--cw-secondary));
  color: var(--white);
  padding: var(--space-12) 0;
  text-align: center;
  border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
  margin-top: var(--space-8);
}

.contact-section h3 {
  color: var(--white);
  font-size: 1.75rem;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  font-weight: 600;
}

.contact-options {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: var(--space-6);
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.contact-option {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-6);
  text-decoration: none;
  color: var(--white);
  font-weight: 500;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--space-2);
}

.contact-option:hover {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

/* Mobile Optimization */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .confirmation-hero {
    padding: var(--space-16) 0;
  }
  
  .confirmation-hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
  }
  
  .steps-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  
  .details-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  
  .contact-options {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }
}
</style>

{# Confirmation Hero Section #}
<section class="confirmation-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="confirmation-content">
      <div class="success-badge">✓ Registration Confirmed</div>
      <h1>You're In! See You April 9th</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Your registration for the Federal Benefits Workshop is confirmed. We'll send a confirmation email shortly with all the details.</p>
      
      <div class="check-email-notice">
        <h3>📧 Check Your Email</h3>
        <p>A confirmation with the complete agenda and location details is on its way to your inbox.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# Next Steps Section #}
<section class="next-steps-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="steps-header">
      <h2>Before the Workshop</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--gray-600); font-weight: 500;">Three important steps to prepare for April 9th</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="steps-grid">
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <h3>Request Official Time</h3>
        <p>Download and submit your SF-182 form to request official time from your supervisor to attend this professional development workshop.</p>
        <a href="/assets/docs/sf-182-form.pdf" target="_blank" class="step-action">
          📄 Download SF-182 Form
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <h3>Add to Calendar</h3>
        <p>Block your calendar and add the workshop details. Don't forget to arrive 10-15 minutes early for check-in and networking.</p>
        <a href="data:text/calendar;charset=utf8,BEGIN:VCALENDAR
VERSION:2.0
PRODID:-//Capital Wealth//Federal Workshop//EN
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:federal-workshop-april-9-2026@capitalwealth.com
DTSTART:20260409T150000Z
DTEND:20260409T170000Z
SUMMARY:Federal Benefits Workshop - Capital Wealth
DESCRIPTION:Exclusive workshop to maximize your federal benefits: FERS, TSP, FEGLI, FEHB coordination
LOCATION:Weber State University Davis Campus, 2750 University Park Blvd, Layton, UT 84041
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR" download="federal-workshop-april-9.ics" class="step-action">
          📅 Add to Calendar
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <h3>Invite Colleagues</h3>
        <p>Share this opportunity with fellow federal employees. This workshop is designed specifically for Hill AFB and Utah federal workers.</p>
        <a href="/federal-benefits-seminar/" class="step-action">
          👥 Share Registration Link
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# Event Details Section #}
